snippet.title: Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2012 (PS3) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2012, a baseball video game by Konami for PlayStation 3. Rakuten Eagles at Seibu Lions (I can't get enough of Seibu's Belluna Dome, it's too cool during day games).
